thumb.title: Seller’s remorse – what it is and how to handle it
thumb.description: Picture this: You’ve sold your property. You might have even celebrated that sale. But then…the doubts creep in.You begin scouring real estate sites online, wondering if you’ve made the right decision to leave your neighbourhood. You start looking too closely at potential new homes and convince yourself that your old place was probably better.Reference: https://www.conveyancing.com.au/articles/sellers-remorse
